---
title: Vegan Shawarma-Spiced Portobello Skewers with Bell Pepper, Green Beans, Lemony Rice & Hummus Sauce
description: We’re sticking it to boring old meat skewers—literally! This vegan dinner idea makes a point (get it?) for trying something colorful, fresh, and tasty. The earthy portobello mushrooms, bright bell pepper, and sweet red onion that adorn these skewers are coated in a warming spice blend that gives them a delicious depth of flavor as they roast and caramelize. The skewers are served atop fluffy, zesty lemon rice with roasted green beans as well as lemony hummus sauce for dipping, drizzling, and dunking to your heart’s content.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ad6fe29629eec88a416c4f-32529153.jpeg
